Package: metayer
Title: tooling for package development
Version: 0.2.4
Authors@R: 
    person("Dustin", "Lennon", , "dustin.lennon@gmail.com", role = c("aut", "cre"),
           comment = c(ORCID = "0009-0002-8558-8765"))
Description: metayer provides miscellaneous tools useful for package development.  In particular,
    it currently attempts to improve the experience of writing vignettes in jupyter lab and across
    publishing contexts.  It anticipates the need to retrofit scripts by folding `cli` notifications 
    into `logger` log files.  It offers a simple, hierarchical storage container.  And, lastly, 
    it introduces some additional utility functions for inspecting environments.    
